snippet.textDisplay: PLEASE get some Black friends folks! Eat cornbread, collard greens, black eyed peas, grits, etc. - all can be made vegetarian and vegan. 👍🏽 My great grandmother measured everything with a teacup and her hand AND she was legally blind. I learned how to eyeball ingredients at an early age out of necessity. I still measure things, obviously, but it helps to just "know" what a cup, teaspoon, and a Tablespoon look like. IJS.
